data.description: This charming home sitting on 1.719-acres offers 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom. Formal dining room, Office that includes full size closet and could be used as a 4th bedroom, Gated entry, fully fenced in, with a concrete driveway. Custom cabinets and granite countertops with a large breakfast area. Plus a 30 AMP plug for your RV and extra decking in the attic for storage. Located just outside city limits with nearly two acres of land at your disposal, you'll have the freedom to create your dream outdoor oasis.
